metadata.name: PHARAOH OF EGYPT
metadata.description:
‘Pharaoh of Egypt’ is a piece created not only to honor the ancient Egyptian dynasty but also appreciate it.  
A dynasty ruled until it was overthrown or there were no heirs left to rule. There were more than thirty dynasties in the Egyptian history.
‘Pharaoh of Egypt’; pays homage to the twenty-fifth dynasty of Egypt; also known as the Nubian Empire or the Kushite Empire. Those Kushite Kings are commonly referred to as the ‘Black Pharaohs
